text: The Hochtaunuskreis is a Kreis (district) in the middle of Hesse, Germany. It is part of the Frankfurt/Rhine-Main Metropolitan Region. The Taunus mountains cover the district. ==Towns and municipalities== Towns Municipalities #Bad Homburg vor der Höhe #Friedrichsdorf #Königstein im Taunus #Kronberg im Taunus #Neu-Anspach #Oberursel (Taunus) #Steinbach (Taunus) #Usingen #Glashütten #Grävenwiesbach #Schmitten #Wehrheim #Weilrod ==References== Category:Districts of Hesse
